ADEN-11353 Click event not send after clicking on video

comment.body:
The problem with `clicked` event not being sent was caused by `<div class='toggle-ui-overlay/>`  (div with gradient) which overlays the video ad on UAP.

The `pointer-events:none` css property makes the click "fall-through" this object.
